= Sorcery command =

The {{{sorcery}}} command is a menu-driven interface for all [[Sorcery]] scripts.

The menu system of sorcery allows managing [[Grimoire|grimoires]], [[Spell|spells]], and changing features of a system easily. \\ To do it just run:

{{{
# sorcery
}}}

For command line options please read //sorcery(8)// man page.